import { Box, Center, Flex, Grid, Stack, Text } from "@mantine/core";
import React from "react";

const Layout = () => {
  return (
    <Box bg="gray" h={200}>
      <Stack>
        <Box bg="gray.4">
          <Center>
            <Text>Test</Text>
          </Center>
        </Box>
        <Center>
          <Flex>
            <Grid>
              <Grid.Col span={4}>
                <Box w={50} style={{ border: "2px solid #000000" }}>
                  abcd
                </Box>
              </Grid.Col>
              <Grid.Col span={4}>
                <Box style={{ border: "2px solid #000000" }}>
                  Test
                </Box>
              </Grid.Col>
              <Grid.Col span={4}>
                <Box style={{ border: "2px solid #000000" }}>
                  Test
                </Box>
              </Grid.Col>
            </Grid>
          </Flex>
        </Center>
      </Stack>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Layout;
